file.name: formats-custom.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
paths:
  /types:
    post:
      requestBody:
        description: Expected response to a valid request
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/Types"
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK

components:
  schemas:
    Types:
      type: object
      properties:
        _int32:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        _int64:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        _float:
          type: number
          format: float
        _double:
          type: number
          format: double
        _file:
          type: string
          format: file
        _binary:
          type: string
          format: binary
        _password:
          type: string
          format: password
        _byte:
          type: string
          format: byte
        _custom:
          type: string
          format: custom
